## Project Overview
This is a web frontend project I'm creating for an AI Agent python program.

## Background Information
I want this frontend project to allow users to input a prompt, call the AI Agent, display the current task running status to the user, and finally return the results to the user.

## Tech Stack
- ReactJS
- Vite
- Typescript
- TailwindCSS
- shadcn/ui
- sass

